[<p class="sh2"><span>SIGN UP</span> FOR OUR NEWSLETTER</p>, <p>The undercover student reporter, Caleb Ecarma, embedded himself in the group for several weeks, getting to know the key players <a href="/web/20161020174509/http://www.breitbart.com/milo/2016/10/18/clemson-anti-milo-protester-would-donate-bail-to-anyone-who-put-a-bullet-in-milos-head/">who he names in his piece for\xa0<em>Breitbart\xa0</em>here.</a></p>, <p class="sh2"><span>SIGN UP</span> FOR OUR NEWSLETTER</p>, <p>According to the audio recordings, the\xa0committee is composed of students as well as a university philosophy professor, <a href="/web/20161020174509/http://www.clemson.edu/caah/departments/philosophy-religion/people/facultyBio.html?id=386">Todd May</a>, whilst organisers behind the committee\xa0are rather ironically named \u201cThe Clemson Chapter of Students for a Democratic Society.\u201d</p>, <p>The alleged objective of the committee is to coordinate a large protest against Milo\u2019s talk at the university, with undercover audio recorded suggesting the chapter are enlisting the support of university communications professor Chenjerai Kumanyika, who is also the \xa0leader of a Black Lives Matter spin-off movement, to organise the protest.</p>, <p><iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="557" src="/web/20161020174509if_/https://www.youtube.com/embed/S2d4C8lZvAs?feature=oembed" width="990"></iframe></p>, <p>\u201cOkay, so we\u2019re going to have, like, an event planning committee that\u2019s just going to, like, organize around this Milo thing, so we can work together,\u201d a girl can be heard saying in the recording.</p>, <p>\u201cI don\u2019t think anyone likes Milo, except conservatives who want to use him as their token gay person,\u201d she claims.</p>, <p>Some of the groups invited to participate in the protest include the Black Lives Matter spin-off movement See The Stripes, the Clemson Feminist Club, as well as the Sexuality and Gender Alliance.</p>, <p>However,\xa0students at Clemson University have been planning protests <a href="/web/20161020174509/http://www.breitbart.com/milo/2016/08/11/clemson-students-already-planning-milo-protests-two-months-talk/">since August</a>, with students demanding that the event be \u201cshut down,\u201d as it is nothing more than a \u201cwhite power rally.\u201d</p>, <p>\u201cWe don\u2019t need any more racist, sexist, xenophobic bigots here at Clemson. We already have enough. I\u2019ve already begun the protest planning\u2014drums, whistles, posters, and chants,\u201d another person <a href="/web/20161020174509/http://www.campusreform.org/?ID=7985">said at the time</a>.</p>, <p><em>You can follow Ben Kew <a href="/web/20161020174509/https://www.facebook.com/benjkew/?skip_nax_wizard=true" target="_blank">on Facebook</a>, on Twitter at </em><em><a href="/web/20161020174509/https://twitter.com/ben_kew" target="_blank">@ben_kew</a>,\xa0or\xa0email him at bkew@breitbart.com\xa0</em></p>]